Category,Action,Method,Endpoint,Body Requirements
Auth,Signup,POST,/api/auth/signup,"username, email, password"
Auth,Login,POST,/api/auth/login,"email, password"
Auth,Get Profile,GET,/api/auth/me,Requires Bearer Token
Chat,Get History,GET,/api/messages/:id,:id is the other user's ID
