Chat,Edit,PUT,/api/messages/edit/:id,":id is message ID, body: text"
Chat,Delete,DELETE,/api/messages/delete/:id,:id is message ID
Chat,Clear All,DELETE,/api/messages/clear/:id,:id is other user's ID